#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:32
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "In this &systemsettings; module you can configure &kde;'s session manager "
#| "and logout settings."
msgid ""
"In this &systemsettings; module you can configure &plasma;'s session manager "
"and logout settings."
msgstr ""
"W tym module &systemsettings-dopelniacz; możesz skonfigurować menedżera "
"sesji &kde; oraz ustawienia wylogowania."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:35
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Session management refers to &kde;'s ability to save the state of "
#| "applications and windows when you log out of &kde; and restore them when "
#| "you log back in."
msgid ""
"Session management refers to &plasma;'s ability to save the state of "
"applications and windows when you log out of &plasma; and restore them when "
"you log back in."
msgstr ""
"Termin <quote>zarządzanie sesjami</quote> w &kde; odnosi się do możliwości "
"zapisywania stanu programów i okien podczas wylogowania z &kde; oraz "
"przywracania stanu po powtórnym zalogowaniu."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:40
#, no-c-format
msgid "General"
msgstr "Ogólne"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:43
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ask for confirmation: on shutdown, restart, and logout"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:45
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this setting is turned on, the logout confirmation screen will be shown "
"when you log out, shut down, or restart. When the setting is turned off, "
"your computer will log out, shut down, etc. immediately after clicking the "
"respective button."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:52
#, no-c-format
msgid "On login, launch apps that were open"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:53
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "You may choose one of three options on what should happen when you log "
#| "into &kde;:"
msgid ""
"You may choose one of three options on what should happen when you log into "
"&plasma;:"
msgstr ""
"Możesz wybrać jedną z trzech opcji, określających zachowanie podczas "
"logowania do &kde;:"

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:58
#, no-c-format
msgid "On last logout"
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:59
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If this option is checked, &kde; will save your current session's state "
#| "when you logout. &kde; will restore your session on the next login, so "
#| "you can continue to work with a desktop just like you left it."
msgid ""
"If this option is checked, &plasma; will save your current session's state "
"when you logout. &plasma; will restore your session on the next login, so "
"you can continue to work with a desktop just like you left it."
msgstr ""
"Jeżeli wybraną tę opcję, &kde; zachowa stan Twojej bieżącej sesji przy "
"wylogowaniu i odtworzy ją podczas następnego logowania, tak aby można było "
"kontynuować przerwaną wcześniej pracę."

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:65
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Restore manually saved session"
msgid "When session was manually saved"
msgstr "Przywróć zapisaną sesję"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:66
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Instead of restoring &kde; to the state it was when you logged out last, "
#| "it will be restored to a specific state that you have saved manually."
msgid ""
"Instead of restoring &plasma; to the state it was when you logged out last, "
"it will be restored to a specific state that you have saved manually."
msgstr ""
"Zamiast przywracać &kde; do stanu, jaki był przy wylogowaniu, przywraca "
"sesję do określonego stanu, który został zapisany przez Ciebie ręcznie."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:68
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A <guilabel>Save Session</guilabel> button will appear in the "
"<guilabel>Application Launcher</guilabel> menu and &plasma; search. When you "
"click it, &plasma; will remember the apps that are open and restore them on "
"the next login. Click it again to replace the set of remembered apps."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: guilabel
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start with an empty session"
msgstr "Uruchom pustą sesję"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:73
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "If you choose this option, &kde; will never restore sessions that it has "
#| "saved."
msgid ""
"If you choose this option, &plasma; will never restore sessions that it has "
"saved."
msgstr ""
"Jeżeli ta opcja została wybrana, &kde; nie będzie przywracać zapisanych "
"sesji."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:77
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "Finally, you can enter a colon (<literal>:</literal>) or comma (<literal>,"
#| "</literal>) separated list of applications that should not be saved in "
#| "sessions, and therefore will not be started when restoring a session. For "
#| "example <userinput>xterm:konsole</userinput> or <userinput>xterm,konsole</"
#| "userinput>."
msgid ""
"Finally, you can enter a colon (<literal>:</literal>) or comma (<literal>,</"
"literal>) separated list of applications that should be excluded from "
"sessions, and therefore will not be started when restoring a session. For "
"example <userinput>xterm:konsole</userinput> or <userinput>xterm,konsole</"
"userinput>."
msgstr ""
"Na końcu można podać listę programów (rozdzielonych znakiem <literal>:</"
"literal> lub przecinkiem <literal>,</literal>), które nie powinny być "
"zachowywane w danej sesji i nie mają być przywracane po ponownym logowaniu. "
"Na przykład <userinput>xterm:konsole</userinput> lub <userinput>xterm,"
"konsole</userinput>."

